toris-packages、apps/studioV2 app/api 与 page/bis/ajaxProxy","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":135,"content":"允许修改：上述 + tests/** + docs/AI/** + 本批里程碑勾选；删除本步清零范围内的 mock 文件","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":136,"content":"禁止落点：Host 闭环、debugger 深化、mock 双轨、以 CanvasMockGraph/MOCK_* 为业务真源、无引用兼容壳","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":137,"content":"状态不变量：Content 在 data/；保存后刷新可见；整包保存；清零域无业务 mock 入口","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":138,"content":"verify：npm run quality:studio","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":139,"content":"```","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":140,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":141,"content":"---","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":142,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":143,"content":"## 1. 任务表","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":144,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":145,"content":"| 状态 | ID | 任务 | verify |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":146,"content":"|------|-----|------|--------|","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":147,"content":"| ✅ | V2-T3-1 | **角色落盘**：正式五人写入 `data/characters/*.json`（agentId 与 personalityCode 对齐 docs/AI）；可与 golden 样例并存 | npm run quality:studio |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":148,"content":"| ✅ | V2-T3-2 | **第一幕真包**：新建 `data/storis-packages/wrong_number_act1/`（story.conf + 三张 s-card + canvas.layout）；叙事对齐 docs/AI 拓扑蓝本；packageId 禁用内存条旧名 | npm run quality:studio |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":149,"content":"| ✅ | V2-T3-3 | **角色 CRUD + 删 mock**：列表/新建/删除/详情与编辑器角色弹窗全部 `/api/characters`；**同一任务内**删除 MOCK_CHARACTERS/mockCharactersData/listMockCharacters/commitUpdateCharacterMock 等业务入口与无引用文件 | npm run quality:studio |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":150,"content":"| ✅ | V2-T3-4 | **玩家 CRUD + 删 mock**：验收 `/api/users` 增删改刷新仍在；**同一任务内**删除 listMockUserProfiles/MOCK_USER_PROFILES 作列表或增删真源的残余 | npm run quality:studio |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":151,"content":"| ✅ | V2-T3-5 | **故事包 BFF**：列包/读包/整包写回 `data/storis-packages`；与 golden_handoff 格式兼容；server 落点遵守 V2 目录规则 | npm run quality:studio |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":152,"content":"| ⬜ | V2-T3-6 | **列表与编辑器读写 + 删 mock**：列表与打开均读盘；保存写盘；**同一任务内**去除 MOCK_STORY_PACKAGES/mockWorkbench/CanvasMockGraph 作为列表或打开真源；无引用种子删除或仅留测试夹具 | npm run quality:studio |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":153,"content":"| ⬜ | V2-T3-7 | **编辑接线**：浮窗/出口/Effect/归属可保存落盘；锚点对齐磁盘角色；清理编辑器仅 mock 且已无引用的合并/种子函数 | npm run quality:studio |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":154,"content":"| ⬜ | V2-T3-8 | **收口**：需求验收勾选；更新 docs/AI 为真源+已删 mock；抽查清零范围无业务引用残余 | npm run quality:studio |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":155,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":156,"content":"---","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":157,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":158,"content":"## 2. 批次出口（每批结束后）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":159,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":160,"content":"- 本批任务行均为 ✅","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":161,"content":"- 任务 `verify` / `verify_default` exit 0","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":162,"content":"- Reviewer：`{workflow_dir}/reviews/latest.json` 中本轮 `blocker=0` 且 `critical=0`","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":163,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":164,"content":"额外关注：","conten